narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Cross Country Staffing Inc. is a In Home Supportive Care provider based in Hialeah, FL. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $43.9M in Medicaid payments across 364K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $43.9M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
